data.description: Unlike any other homes in this neighborhood. NO HOA!!   Beautiful curb appeal. Charming 3-4-bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home situated in a quiet neighborhood in South Houston,Texas. Masterfully Updated in 2020 with modern touches. Large Driveway fits 4 cars easily. Spacious living area. Fully equipped Kitchen with Granite Countertops. Fenced-in backyard with a Covered Patio and a Detached Covered Deck/Patio perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying the outdoors. Laminate Wood Flooring in all living areas. Carpet in Bedrooms. Modern light fixtures and LED lights, Programmable ADT security key pad and wired camera. Easy access to I-45 Freeway, Fiesta Grocery Store and restaurants. Roof and AC very recent. Owned water softener system. Built-in Cabinets. Stylish window coverings.
